{"tid":2477270,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"查理芒格3750萬美元首度入股阿里巴巴","createTime":"2021-04-06T07:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T15:39:30.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"69cb53af82c301eac4f525e3f57a3ef89f3b841b","tid":2477270,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T07:21:09.000Z","msg":"以孟格（Charlie Munger）為董事長的報紙和軟體公司Daily Journal披露首次入股中國網路巨頭阿里巴巴。<br />\n<br />\n據監管機關周一公布的文件顯示，Daily Journal透過美國存託股票（ADS）累積的阿里巴巴持股，截至3月底總計約3750萬美元（約10.7億台幣）。該公司還持有富國銀行、美國銀行（BofA）、浦項鋼鐵（posco）和us bancorp的股份，這些投資自2020年底以來一直沒有變化。<br />\n<br />\n對阿里巴巴的投資佔到Daily Journal投資組合的19%，這是孟格近年最大一筆投資部位。<br />\n孟格是巴菲特所執掌波克夏海瑟威（BERKSHIRE HATHAWAY）的副董事長，是巴菲特是事業夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210406/EZL2OR5JV5E75LCZ5NIFZGVJVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210406%2FEZL2OR5JV5E75LCZ5NIFZGVJVU%2F&d=PGvktPFvO8uhCwWWOTiXtfjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=96d1b73e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210406%2FEZL2OR5JV5E75LCZ5NIFZGVJVU%2F&h=e86cd0d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210406/EZL2OR5JV5E75LCZ5NIFZGVJVU/</a>"},{"pid":"d7fd303853a832780cf4de8ec3752fd30c86b0c5","tid":2477270,"uid":159448,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T07:34:21.000Z","msg":"多數依啲名人入完會陰跌一排 跟住就升到你唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062d697703d23227784f5fc1f89517d8d1ceb0ad","tid":2477270,"uid":274921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T07:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as